Regression Test Cases

TC_1: Headers links should be working correctly
 Test steps:
 1. go to https://www.demoblaze.com/index.html#.
 2.click any of the header links like "home" link.
 3.It should work as expected.

TC_2: Company logo image link should be working properly
 Test steps:
 1.Go to https://www.demoblaze.com/index.html#.
 2.Click on the company logo "product store" which is located  on the top left.
 3.It should refresh the page.

TC_3: "Home" link should take the user to homepage when clicked
 Test steps:
 1.Go to https://www.demoblaze.com/index.html#.
 2.click on the "Home" link located in the header.
 3.Verify the system should take you on the main page if you are on the other page.

TC_4: Contact link should open a popup window
 Test steps:
 1.Go to https://www.demoblaze.com/index.html#.
 2.click on the contact link located in the header.
 3.Verify the pop up window is shown.

TC_5: About Us link should open a popup window with a video
 Test steps:
 1.Go to https://www.demoblaze.com/index.html#.
 2.click on the "About us" link located in the header.
 3.Verify the pop up window is shown and user can see a video.

TC_6: Cart link should open a separate cart page
 Test steps:
 1.Go to https://www.demoblaze.com/index.html#.
 2.click on the "cart" link located in the header.
 3.verify the system should take user to separate page.

TC_7: Log in button should open a popup window to log into the system
 Test steps;
 1.Go to https://www.demoblaze.com/index.html#.
 2.click on the "log in" button located in the header.
 3.verify the popup window is shown with username and password.

TC_8: Sign up button should open a popup window to log into the system
 Test steps:
 1.Go to https://www.demoblaze.com/index.html#.
 2.click on the "sign up" button located in the header.
 3.verify the popup window is shown with username and password.

TC_9: Carousel images should be changed automatically every 3 second
 Test steps:
 1.Go to https://www.demoblaze.com/index.html#.
 2.Notice the carousel images should change in every 3 seconds.

TC_10: Left and right arrow buttons should change the carousel images accordingly
 Test steps:
 1.Go to https://www.demoblaze.com/index.html#.
 2.click on the left arrow button located beside the carousel image.
 3.verify the carousel image should change.
 4.click on the right arrow button located beside the carousel image.
 5.verify the carousel image should change.
